body.body: Service tools have been developed to facilitate removal, dismantling and assembly of certain mechanical components in a practical manner without causing damage. Some operations on Triumph Motorcycles cannot be carried out without the aid of the relevant service tools. Where this is the case, the tools required will be described during the procedure in the relevant service manual.

This document lists all current service tools supplied as part of the dealer service kit T3880110. Some service tools for older models have been removed from this kit and from the latest tool board overlays. These older tools can be ordered through the EPC if required.
